{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC04_JUR_820.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1b,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x129,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Wait, Ayesha... Look..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "That's...the dragon! So he was here...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x12b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. I've finally come to a place where I can almost reach up and grab its throat."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "From here on out is the domain of the dragon. Each step forward will require determination."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "You don't need to tell me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Even amongst dragons, possessing both wisdom and power, this ancient dragon is worthy of being called the strongest."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "And that's him. I find him to be a worthy opponent."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I know now might not be the time to ask a question like this, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Why do you want to defeat this dragon, Juris?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "This really isn't the time to ask, but well, I guess that's so like you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "...His claws have taken numerous lives, and the fire he breathes has burned a number of towns."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "So you're saying...that you're fighting to protect the residents of those towns?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x194,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "No. I don't think I'm challenging the dragon just because exterminating harmful creatures is a huntsman's job."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I'm not a hero, so it's also different than fighting for a cause."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Well...I have no particular reason."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Y-You don't have a reason, but you're still gonna fight it!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Being born in a village of huntsmen,<CR>I grew up watching other huntsmen."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "In our village, we have a tradition. Anyone who hunts a dragon, the species that rises above all creatures..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Is a true huntsman."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x196,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "However, our reality is much different. Basically, no one goes after something that they aren't sure can be hunted."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Huntsmen have lives, too. As well as, things they need to protect."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "For you, that's Nanaca."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Right. Even so, there used to be<CR>someone...in my family who hunted<CR>dragons."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Being raised on the old stories of my ancestors, it became my dream to hunt dragons."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "There is no reason for me to hunt him.<CR>I just want to fulfill my dream."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I'm glad I asked. I feel like I was able to find a little more determination."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x12,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "I see...<CR>...Now, let's go!"
        }
    ]
}